PD Playlist is Monthly Indie Rock Playlists
Sequenced and Divided by Tempo:

Plus (+) Playlist = Uptempo tracks
Minus (-) Playlist = Downtempo tracks

Playlists are sequenced (ordered) for an uninterrupted,
continuous listen. Songs are generally ordered by
common characteristics. Playlist are divided and
ordered in the hopes that listeners can simply use the playlist files (m3u, pls or wpl) listen, and enjoy.

So, Plus (+), Minus (-), and track position in the
playlist does not denote any preference but rather
a way to seperate and order the songs.
